⚔️ Aether Blade: Fragmented
Genre: Top-Down Action Rogue-lite
Engine: Godot 4.4.1
Platform: PC

🎮 Core Gameplay Loop
Fight → Loot → Fight → Upgrade → Die → Repeat
- Enter a room, defeat all enemies to progress
- Collect Gold and Blue Mana Shards
- Spend Gold at shops for temporary boosts
- After dying, receive Shards based on performance
- Use Shards for permanent companion/equipment unlocks via Gacha

🧙 The Player: The Water Mage
Abilities:
- Normal Attack: Fires a water ball (no cooldown)
- Passive (Mana Overload): Every 4th attack fires 3 water balls in a 
  parabolic burst instead of 1
- Skill E (Tidal Field): Summons a water circle for 5 seconds. 
  Heals player 10 HP/sec, damages enemies inside. CD: 10s
- Skill Q (King's Call): Summons up to 5 water slimes (1 every 2s) 
  that chase enemies. Grants +20% attack for 30s. Slimes mirror 
  player stats at 30%. CD: 45s
- Dash (Shift): Double dash with invincibility frames, water splash 
  effect. Each charge recovers after 3.5s
- Hold Attack + Move Mouse: Places ice spikes on map (max 10, 
  or 25 with Frozen Arsenal modifier)
- R Key: Recalls all placed ice spikes, dealing pass-through damage 
  to enemies on return path

📊 Player Stats
HP: 100 | Base ATK: 10 | Crit Rate: 5% | Crit DMG: 150%
Move Speed: 300 | Energy Max: 100

🌀 Rogue-lite Systems

🏠 Room System
- 3 rooms (room1, room2, room3) randomized per run
- Each room has enemy zones with auto-spawning enemies
- Room clear triggers portal appearance
- Portal gives choice: End Run or Continue (with death penalty risk)

💰 Economy
Gold: Dropped by enemies (Normal: 3-10, Elite: 11-20, Boss: 0)
     Used for shop purchases
Blue Mana Shards:
- Room first clear: 200 shards
- Room repeat clear: 50 shards  
- Boss kill: 40 shards
- Iron Will modifier bonus: +30 per room
- Skip modifier: doubles run rewards
- Used for Gacha pulls

⚠️ Death Penalty
- Dying loses 10-40% of run-earned gold and shards
- Scales: 10% per room cleared, capped at 40%
- Only affects earnings from current run, not pre-run inventory

🎲 Modifier System (chosen each room after loading)
Current Room Modifiers:
1. Blood Money: +80% gold, -5% max HP/3s DoT
2. Glass Cannon: +200% damage, enemies 30% faster
3. Plague Pact: Player and enemies take 5% max HP damage/3s
4. Shielded Fury: +20% max HP shield per kill, +10% dmg while shielded
5. Inverted Soul: Healing damages, damage heals
6. Worthy Opponents: All enemies become elite, +30% rewards
7. Living on Edge: Start at 1HP, gain 10% max HP shield per kill
8. High Stakes: Double rewards, guaranteed boss spawn
9. Frozen Arsenal: Ice spike cap increased to 25

Whole Run Modifiers:
1. Berserker: +100% damage, max HP reduced to 30%
2. On a Roll: +7% attack per kill, resets on hit
3. Endless Growth: +10% damage per kill, no cap
4. Iron Will: Cannot heal, +30 shards per room

Special (10% chance):
- Skip: No modifier, double rewards at end of room

🌍 Map Events (triggered after modifier choice, current room only)
- None (50% chance): No effect
- Rainstorm (12.5%): +700% attack/HP, +400% speed, rain visual, 
  slimes are 1.4x bigger and 3x stronger
- Extra Darkness (12.5%): Spotlight radius shrinks
- Blood Moon (12.5%): All enemies +20% HP/ATK/Speed, red tint
- Frost Zone (12.5%): Slippery movement, snow visual, blue tint

👾 Enemy System
Enemies use StatsComponent for all stats.
Zone System: EnemyZone (Polygon2D shapes) + ZoneDetector component
GroupZone: Auto-injects ZoneDetector into child enemies

Enemy Types:
- Glitch (Normal): Melee chaser, low HP
- Bird/Vulture (Elite): Fly-circle + air wave attack pattern,
  air-type color effects
- Golem (Boss): Two-phase boss
  Phase 1: Maintains range, channels stone burst every 4s,
           backs up + shields when player gets too close
  Phase 2: Continuous stone rain, faster when player is close
  Transition: On phase 1 death → 5 incubations scatter on map.
             Player has 30s to destroy them. Each destroyed 
             incubation = 20% less HP in phase 2. If none 
             destroyed = full HP phase 2.

Spawner System (ZoneSpawner + RoomSpawner):
- Normal zone: 4 normal enemies
- Elite zone: 2 elite enemies  
- Boss zone: 1 boss + 2 normal
- Mixed (20% chance): 1 boss + 1 elite OR 1 elite + 2 normal
- Guaranteed 2 elites per room
- Boss guaranteed every 5 rooms or 10% random chance

🐉 Companion System
- Permanent unlocks via Gacha (Blue Mana Shards)
- One companion active per run
- Provide passive buffs (HP, ATK, Crit Rate, Crit DMG, Speed)
- Current companions: Lirien (heal + death block), 
  Grumoss (shield + damage reduction)
- Duplicate pulls → Companion Essence for upgrades

🎰 Gacha System
- Max pity: 70 pulls
- 5-star rate: 1% pulls 1-50, +2.5% per pull from 51+
- Pull 70: Guaranteed 5-star banner highlight
- Every 10th pull: Guaranteed 4-star
- 4-star base rate: 6%

🛠️ Technical Architecture
Autoloads:
- PlayerStats: All player stats + buff system + passive manager hooks
- PlayerInventory: Gold, shards, items, equipment, companion slots
- RunState: Run progress, kill tracking, reward tracking, 
            journal stats, death penalty calculation
- ModifierSystem: Active modifier tracking, effect application,
                  kill/hit/heal hooks, enemy stat modification
- EventSystem: Map event rolling, activation, frost zone physics,
               spotlight control, enemy stat modification
- PassiveManager: Companion passive logic (Lirien, Grumoss)

Components (reusable):
- StatsComponent: HP, ATK, Speed, Crit, Energy for any character
- ZoneDetector: Enemy zone awareness, return-home behavior,
                obstacle avoidance, healing on return
- SkillManager: Player skill cooldowns and casting

Key Scenes:
- res://scenes/globals/ → autoload scripts
- res://scenes/characters/player/ → player + skills
- res://scenes/characters/enemies/ → enemy scenes
- res://scenes/ui/ → HUD, modifier picker, portal choice, 
                     end run screen, event banner
- res://scenes/game/rooms/ → room1, room2, room3
- res://resources/modifiers/ → RunModifier .tres files
- res://shaders/ → spotlight shader
- res://scripts/effects/ → visual effect scripts
                           (rain, snow, dash splash, 
                            ice hit, water hit ripple)
